    General Stores in Mulund, Mumbai

    (1805 Ratings & Reviews) 4.1 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Mulund, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These retail stores are a part of the sales network of most FMCG brands and leading manufacturing companies. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Mulund, Mumbai.
